@rtaylo45 Nice benchmark problems.
If you want to use SUPG stabilization, you need to add all SUPG terms, i.e., TimeDerivative, Forcing Function and Advection Function. In your current input file, you only have Advection SUPG term. See modules/level_set/test/tests/verification/1d_level_set_supg_mms/1d_level_set_supg_mms.i for example.
For this problem, you probably do not need SUPG stabilization. Remove it and give it a shot.
